<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>征集主题</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">“战疫情·新时代文明实践在行动”微视频展播征集</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>征集对象</strong></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
